pageProduct.name: SUP Womens Essentials 30 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

More than a multivitamin - 15 essential nutrients including fish oil to help fill nutritional gaps.

LESS IS MORE
At SUP we have simplified supplements to enable you to take one small step that delivers big results. Many multi vitamins out there don't contain a good dose of essential nutrients, like fish oil. After obsessively studying women's diets and lifestyles, we identified and targeted the 15 essential nutrients for women and wrapped them up in one daily vitality capsule.

WHY POP SUP?
SUP's release-technology capsule enables 15 essential nutrients including a dose of fish oil to be delivered in an innovative, new format. SUP helps:
- Boost energy levels
- Fill nutritional gaps
- Alleviate stress
- Maintain health hair, skin & nails POPSUP

Size: 30 Capsules

KEY FEATURES

• Boost energy levels
• Maintain healthy hair, skin & nails
• Fill nutritional gaps
• Alleviate stress
• Dual Action capsules with fish oil

Warnings

Always read the label. Use only as directed. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Do not use if tamper evident seal Is broken or missing. Vitamins should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Natural fish oil 400mg
- Equiv. to Eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 72mg
- Equiv. to Docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 48mg
DI-alpha tocopheryl acetate (Vitamin E) 10mg
Colecalciferol (Vitamin D 200IU) 5mcg
Retinol palmitate 1.76mg
- Equiv. to Vitamin A 900mcg
Nicotinamide (Vitamin B3) 14mg
Cyanocobalamin (Vitamin B12) 2.4mcg
Magnesium oxide (Heavy) 33mg
- Equiv. to Magnesium 20mg
Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 45mg
Phytomenadione (Vitamin K1) 70mcg
Potassium iodide 196.2mcg
- Equiv. to Iodine 150mcg
Chromium picolinate 201.2mcg
- Equiv. to Chromium 25 mcg
Ferrous fumarate (Iron) 12.2mg
- Equiv. to Iron 4mg
Folic acid (Folate) 400mcg
Calcium phosphate 38.7mg
- Equiv. to Calcium 15mg
Borax 17.6mg
- Equiv. to Boron 2mg

Contains: CONTAINS FISH PRODUCTS

Allergen Contains: Fish

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Peanuts

Directions

Take 1 soft capsule daily with food.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
